org.hibernate.boot.model.domain

Interface ManagedTypeMapping

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EmbeddedValueMapping, EmbeddedValueMappingImplementor, EntityMapping, EntityMappingImplementor, IdentifiableTypeMapping, IdentifiableTypeMappingImplementor, ManagedTypeMappingImplementor, MappedSuperclassImplementor, MappedSuperclassMapping
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    org.hibernate.boot.model.domain.internal.AbstractIdentifiableTypeMapping, org.hibernate.boot.model.domain.internal.AbstractManagedTypeMapping, org.hibernate.boot.model.domain.internal.AbstractMappedSuperclassMapping, Component, JoinedSubclass, MappedSuperclass, PersistentClass, RootClass, SingleTableSubclass, Subclass, UnionSubclass

    public interface ManagedTypeMapping
    Corollary to what JPA calls a "managed type" as part of Hibernate's boot-time metamodel. Essentially a base class describing the commonality between an entity, a mapped-superclass and an embeddable.
